fields.title: BMW M4 Competition Coupe
fields.description: Stunning, low-mileage M4 Competition. Finished in Brooklyn Grey with carbon fiber package. Still under factory warranty. A true driver's car.

fields.title: BMW X5 40i xDrive
fields.description: Executive package SUV, meticulously maintained. Equipped with panoramic sunroof, head-up display, and premium sound system. Perfect family vehicle.

fields.title: BMW M Performance Floor Mats
fields.description: Set of four all-weather floor mats with M Performance branding. Designed for 2019-2024 3 Series models.

fields.title: Mercedes-Benz C300 Sedan
fields.description: Elegant C-Class with AMG styling package. Features heated seats, navigation, and blind-spot assist. Recently serviced and ready for the road.

fields.title: Mercedes-Benz G 63 AMG
fields.description: Brand new, zero-mileage G-Wagon. Handcrafted V8 engine, exclusive leather interior, and all available driver assistance systems. Immediate availability.

fields.title: Genuine Mercedes-Benz Oil Filter Kit
fields.description: OEM oil filter and gasket kit compatible with most M274 4-cylinder Mercedes engines.

fields.title: Toyota RAV4 XLE
fields.description: Reliable and efficient SUV. All-wheel drive, excellent fuel economy, and Toyota Safety Sense 2.0. Perfect condition, single owner.

fields.title: Toyota Corolla LE
fields.description: Highly dependable commuter car. Well-maintained service records. A practical and affordable vehicle known for its longevity.

fields.title: Toyota Land Cruiser 300 Series
fields.description: The legendary off-roader, completely redesigned. Full luxury and capability package. Very limited stock available.

fields.title: Toyota Roof Rack Cross Bars
fields.description: Locking cross bars designed to fit the factory rails on 2019-2023 RAV4 models. Ideal for cargo carriers or bike mounts.

fields.title: Honda Civic EX Sedan
fields.description: Clean, reliable Civic with the fuel-efficient 1.5L turbo engine. Includes Honda Sensing safety features and a spacious cabin.

fields.title: Honda CR-V AWD Touring
fields.description: Top-tier CR-V trim with leather, navigation, and all-wheel drive. Practically new and priced to sell quickly.

fields.title: Honda Accord Hybrid Sport
fields.description: Fuel-sipping hybrid sedan offering a blend of performance and incredible gas mileage. Sport styling package included.

fields.title: Honda Genuine Spark Plugs
fields.description: Set of four OEM iridium spark plugs, factory specification for most 4-cylinder Honda engines (2015+).

fields.title: BMW iX xDrive50
fields.description: Brand new electric SUV with massive range and luxurious interior. Cutting-edge technology and immediate torque. Fully electric.

fields.title: Mercedes-Benz EQS 580 Sedan
fields.description: Flagship electric luxury sedan. Features the impressive Hyperscreen dashboard and exceptional ride comfort. Low miles.

fields.title: AMG Aero Wheel Set (19-inch)
fields.description: Full set of four 19-inch AMG style alloy wheels. Improves aesthetics and handling. Fits most C-Class and E-Class models.

fields.title: Toyota Camry SE
fields.description: Sporty and reliable sedan. Recent model year with minimal wear. Excellent choice for daily commuting and long trips.

fields.title: Toyota Microfiber Interior Cleaning Kit
fields.description: Official Toyota interior cleaning kit, including microfiber cloths, dashboard cleaner, and leather conditioner.

fields.title: Honda Pilot Elite
fields.description: Three-row SUV perfect for a large family. Features heated/ventilated seats, rear entertainment system, and all-wheel drive.
